songs.title: Kung Fu Grip
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
She's got a smile
That I’d die for
Everyone knows, that I’m
A prisoner of war, for her
Yeah

[Pre-Chorus]
Sometimes I wish
I had a kung fu grip
Never let her slip
Away she'd be my girl

[Chorus]
I Really wish she knew
What I feel is true
She'd be my darling
I would be her hero too

[Verse 2]
I’m so in love
With her
Don’t care who knows
That I’m
Ready to fight, ready to go
Just like a G.I. Joe


[Pre-Chorus]


[Chorus]


[Pre-Chorus]

[Chorus]


[Outro]
She'd be my darling
I would be her hero too. [x3]
